  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> Hadarot is a <strong>deckbuilder</strong> where <strong>combat never stops</strong>. The battlefield is always the same, and mistakes accumulate turn after turn. <strong>Every decision matters.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/2dfbc4f70497e8395259cc7ded1accb4.poster.avif?t=1774125095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/2dfbc4f70497e8395259cc7ded1accb4.webm?t=1774125095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/2dfbc4f70497e8395259cc7ded1accb4.mp4?t=1774125095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Persistent cards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>You deploy troops</strong>, towers, and <strong>units with their own health</strong> and <strong>damage</strong> that remain on the field fighting for you. <strong>Decide</strong> which card enters combat, which enemy to attack, and where to position it. One wrong decision can mean defeat, and sometimes you'll have to sacrifice a card to move forward...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/6fbd35e673678fd8413043d5c5d89b4d.poster.avif?t=1774125095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/6fbd35e673678fd8413043d5c5d89b4d.webm?t=1774125095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/6fbd35e673678fd8413043d5c5d89b4d.mp4?t=1774125095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">The danger escalates every turn</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Each turn increases the power of the cards</strong> <strong>you can play</strong> and <strong>the enemies</strong> that will appear... The longer you survive, the riskier and more powerful your decisions become. You will be able to play your <strong>most powerful cards</strong> when you face <strong>the Boss.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/59ca8760f1d06faabff3bca1c9412651.poster.avif?t=1774125095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/59ca8760f1d06faabff3bca1c9412651.webm?t=1774125095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/59ca8760f1d06faabff3bca1c9412651.mp4?t=1774125095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Strategy and Economy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u>Survival depends not only on what cards you have, but also on <strong>how and when you use them.</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Buy and sell cards to adapt your deck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Your coins increase and deplete at the pace of combat, forcing you to plan each turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Adjust your strategy according to the enemies that approach.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Religious Replayability</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u>Your decisions also determine who you will face in the end.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Save the angels and challenge <strong>God</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Embrace chaos and face <strong>Satan</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Take no side and face <strong>Justice</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u>Each route changes enemies, shops, and challenges.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/d45ca5fe31ec7b4ea24efae8a00da255.poster.avif?t=1774125095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/d45ca5fe31ec7b4ea24efae8a00da255.webm?t=1774125095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880080/extras/d45ca5fe31ec7b4ea24efae8a00da255.mp4?t=1774125095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Types of cards </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u>Throughout the game you will find:</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Troops</strong> that fight turn after turn</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Permanent</strong> <strong>passive</strong> abilities that change your game forever</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Actions</strong> and <strong>aids</strong> for critical moments</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Towers</strong> that automatically attack new enemies</p>",
